{"tid":103380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年宵小販續開檔　檔主斥本土派搞事累人","createTime":"2017-02-01T09:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T14:11:45.000Z","uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca71329c9437a9baf514c273a5f0ec56a8f4ad68","tid":103380,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"旺角凌晨經歷暴亂後，晚上約8時，再有小販開檔，現場為旺角山東街附近一條横巷，約有六至七名小販推車仔開檔，販賣熟食，附近有警員巡邏，但未有干涉。一位不願上鏡的小販黃先生表示，「本土派淨係識搞搞震！」，他怒斥本土派搞亂檔，只是借他們「過橋」，阻礙他們做生意。另一位小販蘇先生指，本土派事前並無與他們商量，又認為他們意念出發點是好的，可是太激進。"},{"pid":"0b1ab2df2d9d064bdb7a3d434cf153f91161aad4","tid":103380,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7ea0b4cd31d810fdf0dd7ee5c78408f8751e05","tid":103380,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n自己想搵警察發洩係自己事<br />\n做咩要拖埋小販落水"},{"pid":"171ffff7def61f65ac22d19bf90277790436b792","tid":103380,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"打完齋唔要和尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果上年無咁大壇嘢<br />\n今年佢地會有得開檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59f6c4c00cedb4e4b7c16b8ab64a10d4d579377","tid":103380,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"食環點做野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e0f04239e2b5e76616781acaad417216fb1021","tid":103380,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"回帶"},{"pid":"69ef09db83940b7219bfe577fc0522e604e612bf","tid":103380,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"班小販8成都係廢中同支蝗<img src=