00Z","msg":"本土派又俾人出賣"},{"pid":"6b9aa0fb7e94af8cdc981dc4bdbd5ebc310cd480","tid":103380,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"情況是否有D似<br />\n<br />\n國軍在前線抗日, 共軍係後面搵食<br />\n<br />\n日本退兵後, 共軍聲稱自己趕走日軍"},{"pid":"4d8de44f266bb91a1d416edf5a0985a53fa39f7f","tid":103380,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"過完橋咪抽板囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa05a1a23469b08ada072f4b9fc3a496d0550476","tid":103380,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"唔明點解小販成日比人吹棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又貴又唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8f45ad72a115d22dc1183a5d9e417eb0ebe9bc","tid":103380,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明點解小販成日比人吹棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又貴又唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽人講, 多數都係以下幾個原因<br />\n1. 本土特色<br />\n2. 小販 肯自力更生, 自食其力.......唔似得D蝗蟲, 拎綜援<br />\n3. 三十幾年前, 主要係窮人做小販, 然後D小販靠自己努力, 成功養家, 買樓, 完全符合獅子山下精神, 只要肯捱, 就有出頭<br />\n4. 小販賣平野, 對抗 連鎖餐廳霸權<br />\n<br />\n不過家陣D小販, 好多都係有錢人做, 想搵D外快<br />\n有D就一邊拎綜援 , 一邊做小販<br />\n而且D價錢仲貴過餐廳<br />\n<br />\n已經變左質"},{"pid":"351bade7f76f1e39bfe6ce0d326a6bbe302b934d","tid":103380,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"從來都唔會同情小販<br />\n<br />\n好多小販根本就係黑社會黎"}]}